Title: The Agentic Web [Part 1] with Kevin Scott
Author: Microsoft Events
Description: Join Kevin Scott as he shares insights on the current state of AI, recent advancements, and how to approach a future where helpful agents make AI more useful for developers and users alike. This is part 1 of a pre-Microsoft Build discussion that took place on May 18, 2025. Tune in to part 2 here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bmHJFRNHmoc&feature=youtu.be
